Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.09,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't know what I'd do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:51.64,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Imagine me laughing and now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.56,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}See me walk in the street
