Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.06,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And heaven would find me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:04.19,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'd go on a float
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:08.07,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Eased up, I smile a dream
