Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:30.26,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can free me, I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:33.55,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'm getting so close
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:37.77,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}to laughing sweet with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:38.93,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}(Goin' out on)
